{"tid":113430,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"朱千雪為達哥慶生 講追求者即游花園!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!","createTime":"2017-02-09T03:16:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-09T03:45:58.000Z","uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9bb92bc4ccdf52ee90cc6e5d2849ee0f33ad6997","tid":113430,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T03:16:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/bpnxGg2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FbpnxGg2.png&h=3ff0d720&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n藝人朱千雪到洪水橋，拍攝無綫劇集《踩過界》，並準備了生日蛋糕，為壽星女蔡思貝慶生，千雪表示：「我自己入行以嚟都係喺工作中過生日，呢個班底，王浩信、監製林志華都幫我慶祝過生日，所以我覺得都應該幫思貝慶祝生日。（送咗咩禮物？）蛋糕，佢咁大個人咩都有啦，同埋祝咗佢生日快樂！（知唔知佢有咩願望？）佢話保密，咁希望佢保密嘅願望成真，佢都有話希望《踩過界》收視爆燈，呢個我都希望願望成真 。」 <br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170207/photo/bkn-20170207035703378-0207_00862_001_02p.jpg?20170207135418\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170207%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170207035703378-0207_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20170207135418&h=9cde0c56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朱千雪為好姊妹蔡思貝送上蛋糕慶生。<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/b6KYjb6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fb6KYjb6.jpg&h=ecfbae62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n問到千雪有否介紹男仔予思貝，千雪表示：「唔使啦，係嘛，佢需要咩？我覺得佢個願望唔係呢樣嘢。（你同之前講過嗰個可以交流電影同書本嘅男仔，進展成點？）我未生日，所以未有資格許願新一年有新戀情，而且又要返學又要工作，都冇乜時間，感情方面希望隨緣。」 <br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170207/photo/bkn-20170207035703378-0207_00862_001_04p.jpg?20170207135418\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170207%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170207035703378-0207_00862_001_04p.jpg%3F20170207135418&h=2ce35e06&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ead637f1fa9fdf64b9eceb5ba5b5d57f2aabe894","tid":113430,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T03:21:11.000Z","msg":"達哥原來傷左腳開唔到台<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},